query: SELECT e.id, e.student_id, e.subject_id, e.status, e.enrolled_at, s.name as student_name, sub.name as subject_name FROM enrollments e LEFT JOIN students s ON e.student_id = s.id LEFT JOIN subjects sub ON e.subject_id = sub.id ORDER BY e.enrolled_at DESC LIMIT 20;
